# Temperature sensor drivers
#
menu "Temperature sensors"

config DS18B20
		tristate "DS18B20 Programmable Resolution 1-Wire Digital Thermometer"
		depends on IIO && OF_GPIO
		help
		  If you say yes here you get support for DS18B20
		  thermometer sensor chip connected via 1-Wire GPIO.

		  This driver can also be build as a module. If so, the module
		  will be called ds18b20.

endmenu
